title: Plat 1 Support Looking for serious ranked 5s team
body: Says it all. I'm trying to develop myself as a player both individually and to those around me. Am happy to fit to a schedule as long as it's 100% Otherwise I'll have to sort something out if it's just randomized. Have both skype and teamspeak :) Just Add me Ingame!
